{"word":"G4122 - πλεονεκτέω - pleonektéō - pleh-on-cek-teh'-o - Get an advantage","slug":"G4122","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">πλεονεκτέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>pleonektéō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>pleh-on-cek-teh'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Get an advantage"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C0;&#x03BB;&#x03B5;&#x03BF;&#x03BD;&#x03B5;&#x03BA;&#x03C4;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03C9; - pleonekteo&#x0304;</b> - <i>pleh-on-ek-teh'-o</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G4123\">G4123</a>; to <i>be covetous</i>, that is, (by implication) to <i>over reach:</i> - get an advantage, defraud, make a gain."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G4121\">G4121</a>, <a href=\"#/G4123\">G4123</a>"}]}